    "subtabTitle": "Tuition",
    "subTabDescription": "<p><strong>Tuition</strong></p>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height: 233px; width: 665px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 43px;\">\n<th style=\"width: 78px; height: 43px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Ability</strong></p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"width: 77px; height: 43px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Days / Times</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 49px; height: 43px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Adult (14+)</strong><strong><br /></strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 49px; height: 43px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Child (4-13 years)</strong></p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 75px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 78px; height: 75px;\">\n<p>Complete Beginner</p>\n<p><strong>(never skied before)</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px; height: 75px;\">\n<p>Mon-Fri</p>\n<p>11am - 12:50pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px; height: 75px;\">£185</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px; height: 75px;\">£185</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 21px;\">\n<td style=\"text-align: center; height: 21px; width: 78px;\">\n<p>Beginner</p>\n<p><strong>(able to snowplough turn on baby slope)</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px; height: 21px;\">\n<p>Mon-Fri</p>\n<p>10am - 12:50pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"height: 21px; text-align: center; width: 49px;\">£225</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px; height: 21px;\">£225</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Inghams Exclusive Tuition</strong></p>\n<p>Our exclusive tuition is pre-bookable for children aged between 6-11 and is only available to Inghams guests. Children must be able to parallel turn on easy and medium slopes. Lunch is included in the cost. Guests will be met at the top of the Cretz lift and dropped back to the Hotel De Champoluc at the end of the day.</p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height: 124px; width: 667px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"width: 78px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Ability</strong></p>\n</th>\n<th style=\"width: 77px; text-align: center;\"><strong>Days / Times</strong></th>\n<th style=\"width: 49px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Child (6-11 years)</strong></p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 78px;\">\n<p><strong>Intermediate</strong></p>\n<p>Inghams Exclusive Tuition (lunch included)</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px;\">\n<p>Mon - Fri</p>\n<p>9am - 3pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px;\">from £399</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Private Tuition</strong></p>\n<table border=\"1\" style=\"height: 50px; width: 670px;\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 78px;\">\n<p><strong>Private Ski Tuition</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 77px;\">\n<p>Mon 10am - 12pm</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center; width: 49px;\">\n<p>£120 (1 person)</p>\n<p>£30 each additional person</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div style=\"overflow-x: auto;\">\n<p>Private tuition is available for ages 6+. Bookable for individuals or groups up to 4 of the same ability level.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Tuition information</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Tuition will be available all season </li>\n<li>Group tuition needs a minimum number of guests to take place. Very occasionally these numbers aren’t reached. If you have pre-booked tuition and this happens, the ski school will do their best to offer private tuition to the value of what you had originally booked.</li>\n<li>Snowboard tuition can be booked directly with the ski school - <span>Scuola Sci Champoluc</span></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Prices and supplements are correct at the time of publishing. Up to date prices will be confirmed at the time of booking.</strong></p>"
  },
