    "subtabTitle": "Ski Guiding & Free Ski Away Day",
    "subTabDescription": "<p><strong>Ski Guiding</strong></p>\n<p>Enjoy a stress-free tour of the local ski area and get your bearings on the first morning day of your holiday with a local qualified guide. Get insight into the best runs and places to ski on the mountain as well as some useful pointers along the way to improve technique.</p>\n<p>Groups are maximum 12 people and you must be at an intermediate level, confident and capable of skiing red runs. For just £20 per person, you can enjoy almost 3 hours of guiding. Places are limited, so please call us to book or add via 'My Booking' section of our website. </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong>Free Ski Away Day</strong></p>\n<p>Pre-booked your 6 day lift pass? Great news, this grants you access to ski 2 days in another resorts within the Aosta Valley. Inghams have therefore arranged transport, so you can enjoy a day skiing elsewhere at no additional charge on one of the days - as long as you have a 6 day lift pass. Ski away days are weather dependant and the day and time will be advised locally. Please make sure you sign up before you go by either calling us or adding via 'My Booking' section of our website. </p>"
